data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and cozy house that is ready to move into. This beautiful house has a large kitchen and a new STOVE. Also it has a long counter top that easily seat 6 people to enjoy their meal. The bedrooms are spacious and their closets are a good size. The bathroom that is in the hallway and the one that is in the master bedroom are big. . The master bedroom has a sliding door to the patio. The garage is for two cars and is very spacious. Leaving the garage towards the back yard there is a large patio. Also in the backyard there is a large room that could be used for gym or to store things( permit unknown) The entire yard has stamped cement and is ready to celebrate any birthday. It also has a large roof terrace and a small bar to enjoy a delicious drink.The property has leased solar panel.
